g heart attacks, stroke and trauma. Ambulance personnel work closely with our ER team to ensure that the community has the best emergency treatment available.\r\n\r\nIt is important to know that the ER uses a patient sorting system calledtriage. A nurse assesses your condition to determine what level of care you need. Patients evaluated with the most serious injuries and conditions are treated first. Therefore it is important to<strong>clearly state your symptoms</strong>and/or the purpose of your visit. Read our brochure<a href=\"http://smmc.sx/Portals/0/brochures/ER%20brochure.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How things work in the ER</a>, to learn more about our Triage care system.','24-Hour Emergency','','inherit','closed','closed','','138-revision-v1','','','2017-09-14 09:25:57','2017-09-14 09:25:57','',138,'http://localhost/alijan/2017/09/14/138-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(141,1,'2017-09-14 09:36:32','2017-09-14 09:36:32','{\n    \"icare::icare_service_page3\": {\n        \"value\": \"133\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page_icon3\": {\n        \"value\": \"fa fa-flask\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page4\": {\n        \"value\": \"136\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page5\": {\n        \"value\": \"138\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page_icon5\": {\n        \"value\": \"fa fa-ambulance\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page_icon2\": {\n        \"value\": \"fa fa-hotel\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    },\n    \"icare::icare_service_page_icon1\": {\n        \"value\": \"fa fa-user-md\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','6395e2